<http://www.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/event/34604ADDRVMPJGJLHVPJNCTPBBPPMCLLN>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Blockbuster: Rom-Com Edition";
  schema:description """
	<h2>Thursdays</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Your Favourite Movies… Now With A Romantic Twist!</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Our Blockbuster shows are completely improvised and all about our favourite films and genres – horror, western, sci-fi… you name it! And now for a limited time – we're taking all our suggestions and putting them through a rom-com filter for Love Month!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Can a robot find true love? Will the rival police captains finally admit their feelings for each other during their last day on the force? Come laugh yourself silly at the Blockbuster you know and love, this time with a little more love!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Run time: 90 minutes including intermission.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Rated: 14A<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please Note: as The Improv Centre is a licensed facility, all minors (persons under the age of 19) must be accompanied by an adult.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All physical vouchers must now be redeemed via phone or email. Please contact the box office for assistance.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/files/e14b5d20-4b7f-49c0-87e9-f6a1f9a4f073.jpg\" />
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-02-26T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/files/e14b5d20-4b7f-49c0-87e9-f6a1f9a4f073.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/location/603AMBLCJQMLRJDMDQKBNHDKQPPDPCQLJ>;
  schema:organizer <https://spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/organization/the-improv-centre>;
  schema:url <https://theimprovcentre.ca/shows/>;
  schema:offers _:002da49907ad4172abad71415d1299175397;
  schema:duration "PT90M";
  schema:endDate "2026-02-26T21:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime .

