<http://www.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/event/21201ARBBTMBLNJJTVHKLSDDJRJTLMNRD>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Improv 101: the Fun-Damentals";
  schema:description """
	Have you ever wanted to try improv? Explore fun new worlds with like-minded individuals? We have a class for you! Come and hop into Improv 101, a warm comfortable environment designed to introduce to the improv art form. We go over improv fundamentals, importance of teamwork, and will get you up and on your feet having fun in a stress-less environment. Every answer is the right answer!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Saturday & Sunday 11am-3pm.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All workshops and classes are 19+ only.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This is the prerequisite for Improv 102.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>REFUND POLICY:<span><br/></span>No refunds. Day one and two of training must be taken consecutively in the booked weekend to ensure a trusting and collaborative experience for all students. Completion of course and eligibility for class advancement requires full attendance.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>LOCK OUT POLICY:<span><br/></span>Doors will lock 15 minutes after the class begins. Late comers will not be permitted.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>WAITLIST:<span><br/></span>If a class is sold out for a date you're hoping to attend, you can write in to <span class=\"BoldText\">boxoffice@theimprovcentre.ca</span> to be added to a waitlist. While TIC can't guarantee you'll get a spot, we'll reach out if we can fit you in the class. 
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-03-14T11:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/files/2f1bcad0-bca4-4623-9552-69a86cdbb06c.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/location/603AMBLCJQMLRJDMDQKBNHDKQPPDPCQLJ>;
  schema:organizer <https://spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/organization/the-improv-centre>;
  schema:url <https://theimprovcentre.ca/shows/>;
  schema:offers _:002da49907ad4172abad71415d1299175424;
  schema:duration "PT480M";
  schema:endDate "2026-03-14T19:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime .

