<http://www.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/event/22201AVHLKLNNVQMTJHCGGPHJTVQHKKPM>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Improv for Beginners";
  schema:description """
	<h2>Saturdays</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Time:</span> 3:30pm – 5:30pm<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Ages:</span> 19+<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Level Required:</span> no improv experience is required!<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Workshop Capacity:</span> 20 people<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Cost:</span> $20<span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Max 2 enrollments per email per class</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Are you interested in the art of improvisation? Come learn with us! You’ll be taught the basics of improv in this two-hour workshop that’s geared toward beginners. Come enjoy a fun, friendly and supportive environment to learn the magic of “Yes, And!”<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>We also offer a limited amount of free spots for folks who identify as BIPOC, LGBTQIA2S+, or any other marginalized group. Please email boxoffice@theimprovcentre.ca to inquire.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All workshops and classes are 19+ only.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>LOCK OUT POLICY: Doors will lock 15 minutes after the class begins. Late comers will not be permitted.
""";
