<http://www.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/event/46801ACDBKCSKJDBSGRJBRPHCJBLCKVCG>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "TEST-Supplementary Event";
  schema:description """
	Want to play on our stage? <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Add a game to your purchase and you'll be called on stage to play a game with our performers during your show!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This cannot be purchased for someone else, enthusiastic consent is required for participation. Patron must arrive to the show before the start time, must not be inebriated. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Only 1 available per show.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This is not a seat, this must be purchased in conjunction to a ticket.
""";
