	Tita Jokes Vancouver is a musical comedy revue about our Filipina elders, our Titas. A love letter to our mothers, sisters, Lolas and friends, the show explores Filipina heart ache and resiliency and how we cope through humour, story and song.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">“...an exquisite, hilarious, multi-layered spectacle.”</span><span><br/></span>– Mooney on Theatre<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">“You don’t need to be Filipinx to get all the jokes in this hilarious musical sketch comedy…but you might wish you were!”</span> <span><br/></span>– NOW Magazine<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>About Tita Collective:<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tita Collective is an all-Filipina performance collective composed of award-winning playwrights, comedians, musicians, dancers, theatre makers and actors, based in Toronto, Canada. They explore different mediums to tell the stories about the Filipin* diaspora.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>They have won several awards, including the 2023 Second City Outstanding Comedy Award, 2022 BroadwayWorld Toronto Awards - Best Ensemble Performance (Professional), 2022 & 2023 Just For Laughs Award at the Montreal Sketch Comedy Festival, 2019 Steamwhistle Producers’ Pick at the Toronto Sketch Comedy Festival, Best Newcomer at the Montreal Sketch Comedy Festival, The Second City's Outstanding New Comedy Award, and Patrons’ Pick at the 2019 & 2023 Toronto Fringe Festival. They were featured in the “19 Asian Millennial Women You Should Know” listing by Cold Tea Collective, and in Spotify Canada’s “Need Women” campaign for Women’s History Month.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>They have performed with notable artists including Sam Milby (ABS-CBN/The Filipino Channel), Bob the Drag Queen (Just for Laughs, Toronto), and Monét X Change (Just for Laughs, Toronto)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tita Collective are: AP Bautista, Belinda Corpuz, Ellie Posadas, Alia Rasul, and Maricris Rivera.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>www.titacollective.com<span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tita.collective/\">@tita.collective</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tita Jokes Vancouver</span> is produced by Tita Collective, and co-presented by vAct: Vancouver Asian Theatre Company & The Improv Centre.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This is a Special Show – Restricted vouchers do not apply
""";
