<http://www.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/event/41001AMGNGHKLQLCLRMPJKPQBNDVJPHRD>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "True Story!";
  schema:description """
	<h2>Real life stories spark hilarious scenes born from the mundane and the absurd!</h2><span><br/></span>There’s nothing wrong with oversharing in public, right? Especially if it fuels incredible comedy!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>We get real stories from the audience. Life wins, life fails, weird little moments you thought only happened to you – and turn them into rapid-fire short-form scenes. Your true experiences get the full improv treatment: heightened, twisted, celebrated, and occasionally launched into comedic orbit.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>After intermission, you’ll get a glimpse into the lives of our cast members. They’ll tell you short, true-life stories of their own that the ensemble will build scenes from. If you’re in the improv scene, you’ll recognize this as an Armando. If you’re not, think heartfelt storytelling, playful chaos, and a room full of people realizing that their lives are way funnier and relatable than they originally thought.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This show takes real life and turns the dial toward the absurd, the theatrical, and the downright hilarious! Along the way, you’ll get genuine connection, surprising honesty, and comedy that feels personal. It’s the perfect way to fill your Wednesday with laughs!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Rated: PG<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please Note: as The Improv Centre is a licensed facility, all minors (persons under the age of 19) must be accompanied by an adult.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All physical vouchers must now be redeemed via phone or email. Please contact the box office for assistance.
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-04-15T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/files/4a6e35ce-eeb1-453f-97fb-3223b0802cde.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/location/603AMBLCJQMLRJDMDQKBNHDKQPPDPCQLJ>;
  schema:organizer <https://spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/organization/the-improv-centre>;
  schema:url <https://theimprovcentre.ca/shows/>;
  schema:offers _:002da49907ad4172abad71415d1299175486;
  schema:duration "PT60M";
  schema:endDate "2026-04-15T20:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime .

